title: Florida State Kicker Gets Punked By Miami Players For Warming Up On Their Side Of The Field (VIDEO)
text:
The Miami-Florida State rivalry is biter as the Death Row-Bad Boy feud . The only difference is this football rivalry dates back way longer than just one decade alone.
Their respective territories are marked, and both teams fight for bragging rights as the top team in the state of Florida every season. So when this FSU kicker Roberto Aguayo was warming up alone before the game on the Miami side of the field, the Miami players had to remind him where he wasâ€” with force.
Like Whitey Bulger in the new Black Mass movie to one of his victims, "There's always a choice. You just made the wrong one." Watch as these Miami players get in goon-mode and show him as such.
[via SportingNews ]
